K24 TV and East FM presenter Shiksha Arora is off the market. The bubbly presenter said ‘Yes’ after her long-time boyfriend Salman Manji proposed to her while on vacation in South Africa. "He asked and I said yes. Things just got real, like diamond kinda real. Thank you for making me the happiest girl in the world and for the most special day of my life!" Arora posted. "I can’t wait to annoy you for the rest of our lives. Let’s start with forever now, shall we, Salman Manji ? Starting the decade engaged."